FBIS4-7234 "dreas082_j_94004" FBIS-EAS-94-082 Daily Report 27 Apr 1994 Indonesia SRV Foreign Minister on Refugee Repatriation SRV Foreign Minister on Refugee Repatriation BK2704131194 Jakarta Radio Republik Indonesia Network in Indonesian 1200 GMT 27 Apr 94 BK2704131194 Jakarta Radio Republik Indonesia Network Indonesian BFN [Text] Speaking at Jakarta's Wisma Negara Guest House this afternoon, Vietnamese Foreign Minister Nguyen Manh Cam reiterated his country's commitment to repatriate Vietnamese refugees still held on Galang Island. Even though he did not give an exact deadline for the repatriation, the Vietnamese minister said his government will do its best to find an early solution to the issue. About 8,000 Vietnamese refugees remain at the Galang island holding center.
